SYNTHESIS 3: WHAT THREE NUMBERS DEFINE A TOURNAMENT?
  H alone captures ~27% of tournament info.
  (H, score_seq) captures ~33%.
  (H, score_seq, c3) captures more.
  What is the MINIMAL set of invariants that determines the class?
